data.description: Exquisite Colonial situated on 20 acres with an incredible view! This 5 bed/6 bath home truly has it all, from the hilltop horse barn, to the in-ground pool with attached pool-house/guest suite. Inside the main homes 1st floor you will find beautifully detailed woodwork, a formal dining room, a kitchen with granite counter-tops that opens up to a bright sun-room equip with heated tile flooring and an incredible Primary Bedroom Suite with 2 fireplaces, stainless steel soaking tub, walk-in shower and a sauna! The 2nd floor has three good sized bedrooms, 2 full-bathrooms and a shared balcony overlooking the outdoor pool/patio space. The finished basement provides lots of additional living space including a complete gym, half-bath, wet-bar and climate control walk-in Wine Cellar. In addition to the horse-barn outside, there's an attached 3-car garage with radiant heat floors, built in freezers and an additional oversized building/garage with kennel space and a fireplace, the possibilities of use are endless! With a few cosmetic updates and some TLC, this diamond in the rough could be everything you’ve ever wanted while being close to everything you need! Happiness is HOMEmade.
